name: 2021 thereshewas
description:
A couple of weeks ago I need to get out, I went to a park feelin' something wired, something strange, like... like if i were Winston from 1984, and then I stop to smoke in an artifial island and I saw her, there... just there, vibin', chillin', like there is no other place to go, but if that would be ok... 
Parque General San Martin, Mendoza, Argentina.
